cs.OS, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.AR. 

The paper describes a lightweight model operating system, which suggests it belongs to the cs.OS sub-category. It also discusses the implementation of the system in portable C and C++, which could fall under cs.PL. The focus on program verification and reproducibility could place it in cs.SE or cs.SY. Finally, the mention of a symbolic executor suggests a possible connection to cs.AR.
